<div class='questionText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
<a class="spoiler" href="/questions/773867-miss-gene-tierney-a-popular-american">This question contains spoilers...</a>
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[Miss Gene Tierney (a popular American actress mainly of the 1940s-50s) contracted German Measles from a too-zealous fan. Her daughter was born with severe disabilities. Later the fan met Tierney again and boasted about meeting her "while sick".<br />Does anyone know if Mrs. Christie was aware of this real-life incident? <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
